      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s basically brand new and has been pampered since day one\u2014not a single scratch or dent to be found! It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh interior smell. I've taken such good care of it, and I'm honestly a little sad to see it go, but it\u2019s ready for a new home. Come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 44900.0,
