    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-quality E46 M3, meticulously maintained for the purist. At its heart lies the S54 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS\u2014both recently serviced to factory specifications with upgraded internals. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a limited-slip differential. Mechanically flawless, the vehicle has undergone proactive rod bearing replacement and comprehensive subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity. The suspension remains tight, utilizing original geometry for that signature analog feedback. This example boasts a factory-fresh finish and an interior devoid of typical wear, representing a rare opportunity to acquire a mechanically sorted, investment-grade icon.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
