    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in showroom condition since the day it was driven off the lot. The exterior finish glows with a deep, mirror-like luster, free from any swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings, thanks to a professional-grade ceramic coating and consistent climate-controlled storage. Inside, the cabin retains that signature fresh scent. The premium leather upholstery remains supple and taut, with absolutely no bolster wear, cracking, or discoloration. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity surround sound system to the intricate ambient lighting and panoramic sunroof, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by master technicians at authorized dealerships. It has never been driven in inclement weather, and the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. Included with the sale are both original master keys, the complete set of owner\u2019s manuals, and the original window sticker. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a flawless, investment-grade example of this model.",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
